</para><para><simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if the example has completed successfully.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE if the example has failed. </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
